make no more offers, useno farther means,

93
00:05:27.500 --> 00:05:29.500
but with all brief andplain conveniency,

94
00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:32.330
let me have judgment andthe Jew his will.

95
00:05:32.330 --> 00:05:35.600
For thy 3,000 ducats, hereis 6.

96
